FW tw filingsI received this note from Barbara Perhaps when you meet with Toby about postings Barbara can be included so we can find out the TW procedure Original Message From Bischoff Barbara Sent Thursday September AM To Paschal Zelda Subject tw filings zelda fyi i type and process all the tw filing and naomi places the information on the intranet as well as coordinates the software that we use if you have any process questions you can feel free to call me at rates tariffs oma phone fax

FW ProofreaderTeb The following message if from our temporary agency regarding a proofreader for the TW tariff Rob wanted to have me print out the tariff from the Unicom database and compare it to a hard copy He said he was willing to pay extra for it However Blair thinks he and I could do this a little bit each day Give me your thoughts FYI she would do only straight proofreading Zelda Original Message From Legros Liz Sent Tuesday September AM To Paschal Zelda Subject Proofreader Hi Zelda I believe we may have a candidate for this assignment Agency said candidate is flexible with pay rate Candidate would prefer but would work for Agency has said that candidate just coming off a long term assignment where she converted a manual to disk or vice versa and then proofread for accuracy Pay rate Bill rate Pay rate Bill rate Please call me at your earliest convenience Thanks Liz LeGros Contingent Resource Consultant CSS Enron Fax

FW United Way contributionsFYI Original Message From Armstrong Julie Sent Monday December AM To McCarty Danny Gadd Eric Dowd Stephen Harris Steven Hayes Robert Hartsoe Joe Kilmer III Robert Corman Shelley Miller Mary Kay Neubauer Dave McGowan Mike W Watson Kimberly Cc Wadle Susan Winters Ricki Robertson Audrey Kovalcik Tammy Paschal Zelda Mann Ruth Van Norden Mike Call Josie Cappiello Deborah Subject United Way contributions There have been many questions concerning the United Way contributions Enron will not be matching the UW donations and many of you have expressed interest in directing your contribution to another charity If you want to make a change or eliminate your United Way contribution please send an email to HR Service Connection and indicate if the contribution was for either or and which payroll period Please note that no one is encouraging individuals to make changesdelete contributions but times have changed and employees have a different situations Thank you
